prompt.title: Embedding for Simplifying Code for Clarity
prompt.content: Key aspects of simplicity include using descriptive variable names, keeping functions short and focused, and avoiding unnecessary complexity. Developers should strive to write code that is self-explanatory and doesn't require extensive comments to understand its purpose.
